text: ohugē janayā aturin ( satyya) pratikṣēpa kaḷa, paramānta dinayē hamu va (gæna) boru kaḷa, tavada melova jīvitayehi ovunaṭa dāyādayan pirinæmū pradhānīhu "mohu num̆balā men minisaku misa næta, num̆balā anubhava karana dæyin ohu da anubhava karayi. num̆balā pānaya karana dæyin ohu da pānaya karayi" yæyi pævasuvōya
